{"type": "article", "id": 29906, "title": "组装式家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-20T23:04:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160720230009DG9QLgyI7HAPWmEt.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>在法国建筑师 <a href=\"http://charliepommier.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Charlie Pommier</a> 眼中，遵循可持续发展生产的木制家具将是未来家具生产的主流。最近，他所带领的工作室推出了一套不需要胶水或者螺丝刀，花上 15 秒进行组装就能用上的折叠型家具系列 Triangle。这个系列包含了一把椅子和两张大小不同的桌子，桌腿、椅腿和椅背都设计成了三角造型，能够轻松地折叠成平板状，便于收纳和运输。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/charliepommier/triangle-collection-high-quality-assembling-furnit\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，椅子的价格为 199 欧元，两款桌子的价格为 265 和 390 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720232504C6GWNtsv9YgIApTf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720232429KcO9lBQuYkSTbPgM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720232429NcTGOhs7yRw5pj0q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720232428lOpPh84jrxIFB7MT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}